    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Straightforward value with plenty of potential. This vehicle is being offered as an affordable option for someone who wants dependable basic transportation, a budget-friendly second car, or a project to make their own. It shows its age and is not a cosmetic standout, but it presents an opportunity to get into a vehicle at a very accessible price. Priced to move and represented with transparency.",
