      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for cheap wheels with plenty of life left in them? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest, budget-friendly option for someone who needs basic transportation, a first project, or a handy spare vehicle. It\u2019s priced to make sense, and with a little TLC it could be a great little workhorse for the next owner. If you want something affordable without the big price tag, this is well worth a look.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly driver with honest wear and plenty of usable life left. The powertrain pulls through the rev range, the transmission engages as it should, and the chassis feels like a great foundation for a commuter, shop truck, or light project build. Not cosmetically perfect, but it presents as a straightforward, mechanically minded vehicle that\u2019s been kept in running order rather than neglected. If you want something affordable with character, practical capability, and room to make it your own, this is a compelling buy.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
