      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A true diamond-in-the-rough with loads of personality, this car has the kind of presence that turns an ordinary drive into a story. It carries the charm of a well-traveled machine and offers a fantastic opportunity for someone who sees beauty in potential. Whether you\u2019re after a budget-friendly runabout, a hands-on project, or a car with unmistakable character, this one invites you to make it your own. Affordable, distinctive, and full of promise for the right buyer.",
